    "We calculate the transmission spectrum in the usual way, this time setting the ``contribution = True`` keyword argument, however. The difference to the nominal transmission spectrum then measures the influence of the respective layers. Note that calculating the contribution function will increase the computation time considerably. We plan to improve the calculation speed of the contribution function soon.
